Warden archons are ursine celestials with human hands. Their role is to watch over the Portals that lead to Mount Celestia. They use divination magic to keep an eye from afar on the activities of the fiends and other dangerous spirits. One rules each of the 196 provinces of Celestia. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planes of Law        
              
                    Book of Exalted Deeds